name: New Issue
text:
LIVE SELECT
    *,
    time::from::millis(timestamp)
FROM webhook_events
WHERE
    webhookEvent = "issue_created"

name: Created Issues
text:
LIVE SELECT
    # *,
    # changelog,
    issue_event_type_name,
    # changelog.items[*].field,
    # changelog.items[*].fieldId,
    issue.fields.customfield_10150,
    issue.key,
    issue.fields.summary,
    time::from::millis(timestamp)
FROM webhook_event
WHERE issue_event_type_name = "issue_created"

name: Issue Updated
text:
LIVE SELECT
    # *,
    # changelog,
    issue_event_type_name,
    # changelog.items[*].field,
    # changelog.items[*].fieldId,
    issue.fields.customfield_10150,
    issue.key,
    issue.fields.summary,
    time::from::millis(timestamp)
FROM webhook_event
WHERE issue_event_type_name = "issue_updated"
